---
Syntax: leave

Voluntarily departs from your clan. On leaving:

  - Your clan colors are destroyed.
  - All clan job flags (leader, armourer, diplomat, etc.) are cleared.
  - You are removed from the clan roster.

You must spell the command out fully — typing @@yleav@@g will remind you to
use the full word.

See also: clan clist home
